---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Terms of Use" description="Nithan Terms of Use" lang="en">
  <main class="container" style="max-width:760px; padding-top:3rem; padding-bottom:5rem;">
    <h1 style="font-family:'Mali',cursive; color:var(--gold); margin-bottom:2rem;">Terms of Use</h1>
    <div class="policy-content">
      <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>By accessing Nithan, you agree to read and accept all terms stated on this page. If you do not accept these terms, please refrain from using the website.</p>
      <h2>2. Copyright and Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>All content on Nithan — including text, images, logos, and design — is protected under copyright law:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Original stories</strong> are the copyright of Nithan and may not be reproduced without written permission.</li>
        <li><strong>Stories adapted from public domain works</strong> — the original narrative is public domain, but our adaptation and translation are copyright Nithan.</li>
        <li><strong>Logo and brand identity</strong> are the property of Nithan and may not be used without permission.</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>3. Permitted Use</h2>
      <p>You may use Nithan to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Read stories for personal entertainment and educational purposes</li>
        <li>Share links to pages to recommend to others</li>
        <li>Use with family and in educational institutions</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>4. Prohibited Use</h2>
      <p>You may not:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Copy, reproduce, or distribute content without written permission</li>
        <li>Use content for commercial purposes</li>
        <li>Modify or create derivative works from our content</li>
        <li>Use the site in ways that harm the website or other users</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>Nithan is provided "as is" without any warranties. We are not liable for any damages arising from the use of this website.</p>
      <h2>6. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
<style>
  .policy-content h2 { font-family:'Mali',cursive; font-size:1.1rem; color:var(--gold); margin:2rem 0 0.6rem; }
  .policy-content p { margin-bottom:0.8rem; line-height:1.9; }
  .policy-content ul { margin:0.4rem 0 0.8rem 1.5rem; line-height:2; }
  .policy-content strong { color:var(--gold); }
</style>
